      <text>Free-text proof with equivalence reasoning.</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<div class="stack-comment">
<h2>Free-text input</h2>In some situations you can work line by line, as with the first answer in this question.  STACK gives immediate feedback on whether lines are equivalent, allowing students to enter their complete answer.  The second input is free text, allowing students to type in their proof free-form.  This question is not automatically assessed, rather it is human marked.
</div>
<p> (a). Show that \((2n - 1)^2 + (2n + 1)^2 = 8n^2+2\), where \(n \in\mathbb{N}\). </p>
<p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>
<p> (b). Hence, or otherwise, prove that the sum of the squares of any two consecutive odd.</p>
<div class="free-text-container">
[[input:ans2]]
[[validation:ans2]]
[[ascii input="ans2"]]
[[/ascii]]
</div>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
