ta2:"Note that `(2n - 1)` and `(2n + 1)` are consecutive odd numbers.  The sum of the squares of any two consecutive off numbers is therefore
`
(2n - 1)^2 + (2n + 1)^2 = 8n^2+2 = 2(n^2+1)
